<template>
    <v-app>
        <CustomAppBar />
        <v-main>
            <AlertComponent :alertText="alertText" :btnText="alertBtnText"/>
            <BannerComponent :bannerHeight="'70%'" :bannerImage="bannerImageUrl" :slogan="bannerSloganText" :description="bannerDescriptionText"
                :btn_text="bannerBtnText" />
            <DescriptionComponent :title="descriptionTitle" :description="descriptionText" :linkText="descriptionLinkText"
                :linkUrl="descriptionLinkUrl" :imageUrl="descriptionImageUrl" :imagePosition="descriptionImagePosition" />
        </v-main>
        <router-view></router-view>
    </v-app>
</template>

<script>
import AlertComponent from '../components/AlertComponent.vue';
import CustomAppBar from '../components/CustomAppBar.vue';
import BannerComponent from '../components/BannerComponent.vue';
import DescriptionComponent from '../components/DescriptionComponent.vue';

export default {
    name: 'HomePage',
    components: {
        AlertComponent,
        CustomAppBar,
        BannerComponent,
        DescriptionComponent
    },
    data() {
        return {
            alertText: `Google is committed to advancing racial equity for Black communities.`,
            alertBtnText: `See how.`,
            bannerImageUrl: `https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/KWN57FdsV14gg-DtL97jCSdSfd8Y1Hzr5DD01uGP1dF_XR2lJ3EUIu75oeQUOYUmxJcDr4SZ04DmOO6TuaG5P1shLAKNVXFaRPN5Imtq4y0nb2RCUQ=s1500`,
            bannerSloganText: `Faster, smarter marketing`,
            bannerDescriptionText: `Introducing Google Marketing Platform, a unified advertising and analytics platform for smarter marketing and better results.`,
            bannerBtnText: `Sign in to Google Marketing Platform`,

            descriptionTitle: `Easy-to-use tools for small business.`,
            descriptionText: `Google Marketing Platform brings together your advertising and analytics to help you make quality customer connections, surface deeper insights, and drive better marketing results.`,
            descriptionLinkText: `Learn about Google Marketing Platform`,
            descriptionLinkUrl: `https://marketingplatform.google.com/about/`,
            descriptionImageUrl: `https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/3Obh_6pdqf49IZBncFJd_-mcVmF5-PgtejBFSmzK8S1OxD4AZMIbQm33z3eob8jwBr0KezXBlr_PJzH4pKQYqDWmcpn3FW-5HE7pqw=s3000`,
            descriptionImagePosition: `right`

        };
    }
};
</script>
